org.spongepowered.api.data

Interface ImmutableDataBuilder<H extends ImmutableDataHolder<H>,E extends ImmutableDataBuilder<H,E>>

  • Type Parameters:
    H - The type of ImmutableDataHolder
    E - The extended ImmutableDataBuilder
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataBuilder<H>, ResettableBuilder<H,DataBuilder<H>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BlockSnapshot.Builder, BlockState.Builder, EntitySnapshot.Builder, FluidStackSnapshot.Builder

    public interface ImmutableDataBuilder<H extends ImmutableDataHolder<H>,E extends ImmutableDataBuilder<H,E>>
extends DataBuilder<H>
    A builder, much like a normal DataBuilder except that it builds ImmutableDataHolders. While the ImmutableDataHolder is like a DataHolder, it is immutable.
